      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the exhaustion behind your words, but please know that this feeling of peace is often a symptom of overwhelming pain, not a sign that ending it is the right choice. If you are feeling this way, reaching out to a crisis line like 988 or contacting a trusted professional can offer support that feels real rather than performative. There are people who want to help you find a way forward that honors your life and your unique experiences.",
